            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Canopy 0.5.0

- Adds Arc-style Spaces, favorites, native sidebar controls, and trackpad navigation.
- Bundles Jim's Mowing in the native app and restores the signed update workflow.
- Improves browser controls, app icons, graphics behavior, and live FPS reporting.
]]></description>
